sql_statement.static: SELECT FrameSize, Load, OfferedRate, COALESCE(((Rx.L1BitCount)/(Rx.LastArrivalTime - Rx.FirstArrivalTime))*(SELECT DISTINCT (FixedLoad/MbpsLoad) FROM GeneratorConfig), 0.0) AS ThroughputPercent, COALESCE(((Rx.L1BitCount)/(Rx.LastArrivalTime - Rx.FirstArrivalTime)), 0.0) AS ThroughputMbps, COALESCE(((1e6 * Rx.SigFrameCount)/(Rx.LastArrivalTime - Rx.FirstArrivalTime)), 0.0) AS ThroughputFps, COALESCE(Rx.TotalLatency, 0) AS TotalLatency, Rx.AvgLatency AS AvgLatency, Rx.MinLatency AS MinLatency, Rx.MaxLatency AS MaxLatency, COALESCE(Rx.TotalJitter, 0) AS TotalJitter, Rx.AvgJitter AS AvgJitter, Rx.MinJitter AS MinJitter, Rx.MaxJitter AS MaxJitter, TxFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.FrameCount, 0) AS RxFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.DroppedFrameCount, TxFrameCount, 0) AS DroppedFrameCount, COALESCE(100.0 * Rx.DroppedFrameCount/TxFrameCount, 100.0) AS DroppedFramePercent, COALESCE(Rx.ReorderedFrameCount, 0) AS ReorderedFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.OutSeqFrameCount, 0) AS OutSeqFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.DuplicateFrameCount, 0) AS DuplicateFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.LateFrameCount, 0) AS LateFrameCount, TxBitCount, COALESCE(Rx.L1BitCount, 0) AS RxBitCount, COALESCE(LastArrivalTime - FirstArrivalTime, 0) AS Elapsed, TxPort, COALESCE(Rx.PortName, 'NA') AS RxPort

FROM (SELECT Sb.Active AS SbActive, CASE WHEN Sb.FrameLengthMode='IMIX' THEN 'iMIX' ELSE Sb.FixedFrameLength END AS FrameSize, (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS Load, COALESCE(Tx.L1BitCount * (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad / (MbpsLoad * 1e6 * Duration) FROM GeneratorConfig), 0.0) AS OfferedRate, COALESCE(Tx.FrameCount, 0) AS TxFrameCount, COALESCE(Tx.L1BitCount, 0) AS TxBitCount, COALESCE(Tx.PortName, 'NA') AS TxPort, Tx.StreamId, Sb.ParentHnd FROM Streamblock AS Sb LEFT JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS Tx ON Sb.Handle=Tx.ParentStreamBlock) AS SbTx
LEFT JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS Rx ON StreamId=Rx.Comp32 AND (Rx.SigFrameCount IS NULL OR IsExpectedPort) WHERE SbActive

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vsw_tput_iter_agg (FrameSize INTEGER, Load FLOAT, OfferedRate FLOAT, AvgThroughputPercent FLOAT, AvgThroughputMbps FLOAT, AvgThroughputFps INTEGER, TotalLatency INTEGER, AvgLatency FLOAT, MinLatency FLOAT, MaxLatency FLOAT, TotalJitter INTEGER, AvgJitter FLOAT, MinJitter FLOAT, MaxJitter FLOAT, TxFrameCount INTEGER, RxFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFramePercent FLOAT, OutSeqFrameCount INTEGER, DuplicateFrameCount INTEGER, LateFrameCount INTEGER, FloodedFrameCount INTEGER)

SELECT DISTINCT FrameSize, Load, AVG(OfferedRate) AS OfferedRate, SUM(ThroughputPercent)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT TxPort FROM vsw_pkt_loss)) AS AvgThroughputPercent, SUM(ThroughputMbps)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT TxPort FROM vsw_pkt_loss)) AS AvgThroughputMbps, SUM(ThroughputFps)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT TxPort FROM vsw_pkt_loss)) AS AvgThroughputFps, SUM(TotalLatency) AS TotalLatency, 0.01 * SUM(TotalLatency)/SUM(RxFrameCount) AS AvgLatency, MIN(MinLatency) AS MinLatency, MAX(MaxLatency) AS MaxLatency, SUM(TotalJitter) AS TotalJitter, 0.01 * SUM(TotalJitter) / SUM(RxFrameCount) AS AvgJitter, MIN(MinJitter) AS MinJitter, MAX(MaxJitter) AS MaxJitter, SUM(TxFrameCount) AS TxFrameCount, SUM(RxFrameCount) AS RxFrameCount, SUM(DroppedFrameCount) AS DroppedFrameCount, COALESCE(100.0 * SUM(DroppedFrameCount) / SUM(TxFrameCount), 0.0) AS DroppedFramePercent, SUM(OutSeqFrameCount) AS OutSeqFrameCount, SUM(DuplicateFrameCount) AS DuplicateFrameCount, SUM(LateFrameCount) AS LateFrameCount, CASE WHEN (SELECT SUM(SigFrameCount) FROM AnalyzerPortResults)>=SUM(RxFrameCount-DuplicateFrameCount) THEN (SELECT SUM(SigFrameCount) FROM AnalyzerPortResults)-SUM(RxFrameCount-DuplicateFrameCount) ELSE 0 END AS FloodedFrameCount FROM vsw_pkt_loss

SELECT FrameSize AS 'Frame Size (bytes)', Load AS 'Load (%)', TxFrameCount AS 'Tx Frame Count', RxFrameCount AS 'Rx Frame Count', ROUND(DroppedFramePercent, 2) AS 'Dropped Frame (%)', DroppedFrameCount AS 'Dropped Frame Count', OutSeqFrameCount AS 'Out of Sequence Frame Count', DuplicateFrameCount AS 'Duplicate Frame Count', LateFrameCount AS 'Late Frame Count', TxPort AS 'Tx Port', RxPort AS 'Rx Port' FROM vsw_pkt_loss

sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vsw_iter_tmp (IsConverged INTEGER, ConvergedVal FLOAT, CurrVal FLOAT, Resolution FLOAT, MinVal FLOAT, MaxVal FLOAT, InitialVal FLOAT, MbpsFactor FLOAT, FpsFactor FLOAT)
DELETE FROM vsw_iter_tmp

SELECT DISTINCT IsConverged, CAST(ConvergedVal AS FLOAT) AS ConvergedVal, CAST(CurrVal AS FLOAT) AS CurrVal, Resolution, MinVal, MaxVal, InitialVal, Gc.MbpsLoad/Gc.FixedLoad AS MbpsFactor, Gc.FpsLoad/Gc.FixedLoad AS FpsFactor FROM spirent_methodology_RateIteratorCommand AS Ic JOIN RelationTable AS Rt ON Ic.Handle=Rt.SourceHnd JOIN Tag ON Rt.TargetHnd=Tag.Handle, GeneratorConfig AS Gc JOIN Generator AS Gn ON Gn.Handle=Gc.ParentHnd WHERE Tag.Name='RateIter' AND Gn.ParentHnd IN (SELECT DISTINCT ParentHnd FROM StreamBlock)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vsw_tput_iter (FrameSize INTEGER, ConfigRate FLOAT, ConfigRateMbps FLOAT, ConfigRateFps FLOAT, OfferedRate FLOAT, Throughput FLOAT, ThroughputMbps FLOAT, ThroughputFps FLOAT, TotalLatency FLOAT, AvgLatency FLOAT, MinLatency FLOAT, MaxLatency FLOAT, TotalJitter FLOAT, AvgJitter FLOAT, MinJitter FLOAT, MaxJitter FLOAT, TxFrameCount INTEGER, RxFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFramePercent FLOAT, OutSeqFrameCount INTEGER, DuplicateFrameCount INTEGER, LateFrameCount INTEGER, FloodedFrameCount INTEGER, MaxRate FLOAT, IsConverged INTEGER, ConvergedVal FLOAT)

SELECT DISTINCT FrameSize, Load AS ConfigRate, OfferedRate, ROUND(Load*MbpsFactor,3) AS ConfigRateMbps, ROUND(Load*FpsFactor,3) AS ConfigRateFps, ROUND(AvgThroughputPercent,3) AS Throughput, ROUND(AvgThroughputMbps,3) AS ThroughputMbps, ROUND(AvgThroughputFps,3) AS ThroughputFps, TotalLatency, ROUND(AvgLatency,3) AS AvgLatency, ROUND(MinLatency,3) AS MinLatency, ROUND(MaxLatency,3) AS MaxLatency, TotalJitter, ROUND(AvgJitter,3) AS AvgJitter, ROUND(MinJitter,3) AS MinJitter, ROUND(MaxJitter,3) AS MaxJitter, TxFrameCount, RxFrameCount, DroppedFrameCount, DroppedFramePercent, OutSeqFrameCount, DuplicateFrameCount, LateFrameCount, FloodedFrameCount, Ic.MaxVal AS MaxRate, Ic.IsConverged, Ic.ConvergedVal
FROM vsw_tput_iter_agg AS Ag JOIN vsw_tput_cfg AS Cf ON CfgFrameSize=FrameSize, vsw_iter_tmp AS Ic
WHERE Ag.Load=(CASE WHEN Ic.IsConverged THEN Ic.ConvergedVal ELSE Ic.CurrVal END)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vsw_deltaload (FrameSize STRING, ConvergedThroughput FLOAT, Delta FLOAT, CalculatedLoad FLOAT)

INSERT INTO vsw_deltaload VALUES ((SELECT CfgFrameSize FROM vsw_tput_cfg), (SELECT ConvergedThroughput FROM vSwitch_IterationConvergedThroughput WHERE FrameSize == (SELECT CfgFrameSize FROM vsw_tput_cfg)),
(SELECT CfgDelta FROM vsw_tput_cfg), NULL)

UPDATE vsw_deltaload SET CalculatedLoad = (SELECT CASE WHEN Delta < 0 THEN (ConvergedThroughput - (ConvergedThroughput*(abs(Delta)/100))) WHEN Delta > 0 THEN (ConvergedThroughput + ((100-ConvergedThroughput)*(abs(Delta)/100))) WHEN Delta > 0 AND ConvergedThroughput=100.0 THEN ConvergedThroughput ELSE ConvergedThroughput END FROM vsw_deltaload
WHERE Delta=(SELECT CfgDelta FROM vsw_tput_cfg) AND FrameSize=(SELECT CfgFrameSize FROM vsw_tput_cfg))
WHERE CalculatedLoad IS NULL AND FrameSize == (SELECT CfgFrameSize FROM vsw_tput_cfg) AND Delta=(SELECT CfgDelta FROM vsw_tput_cfg)
UPDATE vsw_deltaload SET CalculatedLoad=0.001
WHERE CalculatedLoad < 0.001 AND FrameSize == (SELECT CfgFrameSize FROM vsw_tput_cfg) AND Delta=(SELECT CfgDelta FROM vsw_tput_cfg)

sql_statement.static: SELECT FrameSize, Load, OfferedRate, (SELECT DISTINCT PercentageLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS PercentageLoad, (SELECT DISTINCT MbpsLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS MbpsLoad, (SELECT DISTINCT FpsLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS FpsLoad, COALESCE(ROUND((Rx.L1BitCount/(Rx.LastArrivalTime-Rx.FirstArrivalTime)) * (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad/MbpsLoad FROM GeneratorConfig), 3), 0.0) AS ThroughputPercent, COALESCE(ROUND(Rx.L1BitCount/(Rx.LastArrivalTime-Rx.FirstArrivalTime), 3), 0.0) AS ThroughputMbps, COALESCE(ROUND((1e6 * Rx.SigFrameCount)/(Rx.LastArrivalTime-Rx.FirstArrivalTime), 3), 0.0) AS ThroughputFps, COALESCE(ROUND(Rx.AvgLatency, 3), 0) AS AvgLatency, COALESCE(Rx.TotalLatency, 0) AS TotalLatency, COALESCE(ROUND(Rx.AvgJitter, 3), 0) AS AvgJitter, COALESCE(Rx.TotalJitter, 0) AS TotalJitter, TxFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.FrameCount, 0) AS RxFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.DroppedFrameCount, TxFrameCount, 0) AS DroppedFrameCount, COALESCE(100.8 * Rx.DroppedFrameCount/TxFrameCount, 100.0) AS DroppedFramePercent, COALESCE(Rx.ReorderedFrameCount, 0) AS ReorderedFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.OutSeqFrameCount, 0) AS OutSeqFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.DuplicateFrameCount, 0) AS DuplicateFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.LateFrameCount, 0) AS LateFrameCount, TxBitCount, COALESCE(Rx.L1BitCount, 0) AS RxBitCount, COALESCE(Rx.LastArrivalTime-Rx.FirstArrivalTime, 0) AS Elapsed, SbTx.ParentHnd AS ParentHnd, TxPort, COALESCE(Rx.PortName, 'NA') AS RxPort

FROM (SELECT Sb.Active AS SbActive, CASE WHEN Sb.FrameLengthmode='IMIX' THEN 'iMIX' ELSE Sb.FixedFrameLength END AS FrameSize, (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS Load, COALESCE(Tx.L1BitCount * (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad / (MbpsLoad * 1e6 * Duration) FROM GeneratorConfig), 0.0) AS OfferedRate, COALESCE(Tx.FrameCount, 0) AS TxFrameCount, COALESCE(Tx.L1BitCount, 0) AS TxBitCount, COALESCE(Tx.PortName, 'NA') AS TxPort, Tx.StreamId, Sb.ParentHnd FROM Streamblock AS Sb LEFT JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS Tx ON Sb.Handle=Tx.ParentStreamBlock) AS SbTx
LEFT JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS Rx ON StreamId=Rx.Comp32 AND (Rx.SigFrameCount IS NULL OR IsExpectedPort) WHERE SbActive

report.explanation: Detailed Results for Delta Load Profiling

sql_statement.static: SELECT FrameSize AS 'Frame Size (bytes)', PercentageLoad AS 'Configured Load (%)', ROUND(OfferedRate, 3) AS 'Offered Rate (%)', ROUND(AVG(ThroughputPercent), 3) AS 'Throughput (%)', COALESCE(ROUND(0.01 * SUM(TotalLatency) / SUM(RxFrameCount), 3), 'NA') AS 'Avg. Latency (us)', SUM(TxFrameCount) AS 'Tx Frame Count', SUM(RxFrameCount) AS 'Rx Frame Count', SUM(DroppedFrameCount) AS 'Dropped Frame Count', COALESCE(ROUND(100.0 * SUM(DroppedFrameCount)/SUM(TxFrameCount), 2), 0.0) AS 'Dropped Frame (%)', SUM(OutSeqFrameCount) AS 'Out of Sequence Frame Count', SUM(DuplicateFrameCount) AS 'Duplicate Frame Count', SUM(LateFrameCount) AS 'Late Frame Count', CASE WHEN (SELECT SUM(SigFrameCount) FROM AnalyzerPortResults)>=SUM(RxFrameCount-DuplicateFrameCount) THEN (SELECT SUM(SigFrameCount) FROM AnalyzerPortResults)-SUM(RxFrameCount-DuplicateFrameCount) ELSE 0 END AS 'Flooded Frame Count' FROM vSwitch_IterationDeltaLoadProfilingResults

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vSwitch_AggregateSummaryDeltaLoadProfilingResults(FrameSize INTEGER, Delta FLOAT, PercentageLoad FLOAT, MbpsLoad FLOAT, FpsLoad FLOAT, OfferedRate FLOAT, AvgThroughputPercent FLOAT, AvgThroughputMbps FLOAT, AvgThroughputFps FLOAT, AvgLatency FLOAT, AvgJitter FLOAT, TotalFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFramePercent FLOAT, DroppedFrameCount INTEGER, OutSeqFrameCount INTEGER, DuplicateFrameCount INTEGER, LateFrameCount INTEGER, FloodedFrameCount INTEGER)
SELECT * FROM vsw_tput_cfg

SELECT FrameSize, (SELECT CfgDelta FROM vsw_tput_cfg) AS Delta, PercentageLoad, MbpsLoad, FpsLoad, AVG(OfferedRate) AS OfferedRate, AVG(ThroughputPercent) AS AvgThroughputPercent, AVG(ThroughputMbps) AS AvgThroughputMbps, AVG(ThroughputFps) AS AvgThroughputFps, 0.01 * SUM(TotalLatency) / SUM(RxFrameCount) AS AvgLatency, 0.01 * SUM(TotalJitter) / SUM(RxFrameCount) AS AvgJitter, SUM(RxFrameCount) AS TotalFrameCount, SUM(DroppedFrameCount) AS DroppedFrameCount, SUM(DroppedFrameCount)/SUM(RxFrameCount) AS DroppedFramePercent, SUM(OutSeqFrameCount) AS OutSeqFrameCount, SUM(DuplicateFrameCount) AS DuplicateFrameCount, SUM(LateFrameCount) AS LateFrameCount, CASE WHEN (SELECT SUM(SigFrameCount) FROM AnalyzerPortResults)>=SUM(RxFrameCount-DuplicateFrameCount) THEN (SELECT SUM(SigFrameCount) FROM AnalyzerPortResults)-SUM(RxFrameCount-DuplicateFrameCount) ELSE 0 END AS FloodedFrameCount FROM vSwitch_IterationDeltaLoadProfilingResults

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM vSwitch_AggregateSummaryDeltaLoadProfilingResults JOIN vsw_tput_cfg ON FrameSize=CfgFrameSize AND Delta=CfgDelta

sql_statement.static: SELECT FrameSize AS 'Frame Size (bytes)', Delta AS 'Delta Load (%)', PercentageLoad AS 'Configured Load (%)', ROUND(OfferedRate, 3) AS 'Offered Rate (%)', ROUND(AvgThroughputPercent, 3) AS 'Avg. Throughput (%)', ROUND(AvgLatency, 3) AS 'Avg. Latency (us)', ROUND(AvgJitter, 3) AS 'Avg. Jitter (us)', TotalFrameCount AS 'Total Frame Count', DroppedFrameCount AS 'Dropped Frame Count', ROUND(DroppedFramePercent, 2) AS 'Dropped Frame (%)', OutSeqFrameCount AS 'Out of Sequence Frame Count', DuplicateFrameCount AS 'Duplicate Frame Count', LateFrameCount AS 'Late Frame Count', FloodedFrameCount AS 'Flooded Frame Count' FROM vSwitch_AggregateSummaryDeltaLoadProfilingResults AS r JOIN vsw_tput_cfg ON FrameSize=CfgFrameSize ORDER BY r.rowid DESC LIMIT 1

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vsw_tput_rtchart (FrameSize INTEGER, ConfigRate FLOAT, OfferedRate FLOAT, Throughput FLOAT, DroppedFrameCount INTEGER, OutSeqFrameCount INTEGER, DuplicateFrameCount INTEGER, LateFrameCount INTEGER, FloodedFrameCount INTEGER)

SELECT FrameSize, ROUND(PercentageLoad, 3) AS ConfigRate, ROUND(OfferedRate, 3) AS OfferedRate, ROUND(AvgThroughputPercent, 3) AS Throughput, DroppedFrameCount, OutSeqFrameCount, DuplicateFrameCount, LateFrameCount, FloodedFrameCount FROM vSwitch_AggregateSummaryDeltaLoadProfilingResults AS r JOIN vsw_tput_cfg ON FrameSize=CfgFrameSize ORDER BY r.rowid DESC LIMIT 1

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vsw_tput_rtdeltatable (FrameSize INTEGER, Delta FLOAT, PercentageLoad FLOAT, OfferedRate FLOAT, AvgThroughputPercent FLOAT, AvgLatency FLOAT, AvgJitter FLOAT, TotalFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFrameCount INTEGER, DuplicateFrameCount INTEGER, OutSeqFrameCount INTEGER, LateFrameCount INTEGER, FloodedFrameCount INTEGER)

SELECT FrameSize, Delta, ROUND(PercentageLoad, 3) AS PercentageLoad, ROUND(OfferedRate, 3) AS OfferedRate, ROUND(AvgThroughputPercent, 3) AS AvgThroughputPercent, ROUND(AvgLatency, 3) AS AvgLatency, ROUND(AvgJitter, 3) AS AvgJitter, TotalFrameCount, DroppedFrameCount, DuplicateFrameCount, OutSeqFrameCount, LateFrameCount, FloodedFrameCount FROM vSwitch_AggregateSummaryDeltaLoadProfilingResults AS r JOIN vsw_tput_cfg ON FrameSize=CfgFrameSize ORDER BY r.rowid DESC LIMIT 1
